RelatedSentence: This year 's theme , Vine to Table , will complement the Museum 's Living History Farm as it celebrates its 25th Anniversary at MOR .
All proceeds will benefit the Living History Farm 's programs and operations .
A special live auction item will also be part of this year 's Wine Classic - an opportunity for four people to visit the set of Jurassic World with Jack Horner .
